body_html:
@qianyizhang Are you using a pip package or building from source?

The profiler is current under active development. Hence some features might not be available in pip package yet.

Let me know if building from source still can't solve you problem. tf.contrib.tfprof.ProfileContext() should be the expected API. It is kept in contrib because the API is not stable and might be changed. Once it gets stable, it will be migrated to tf.profiler.ProfileContext
